		<p>

			PERSONA:
			Name: Mike Michael
			Age: 30

			High School : As a high school baseball coach, Mike Michael has a full roster of very energetic and talented players.
			After an intense workout session with his players, he went on the internet so go compare players for his upcoming
			game with a rival team this weekend. Unfortuanately, his results yield very low data on anything. --Fast forward
			after the game:
			Mike Michael after a 5-4 victory again goes to the internet to see what searches he finds on his players and yeilds very
			low results. Mike knows he has very talented kids however no real way of highlighting them on the web.


			USE-CASE:
			Mike Michael, would be estatic on having a respository of reliable player data on both the high school level as
			well as the collegiate level. As a user Mike Michael has professional need for a data driven web site that
			contains data that he could use in order to maximize how he employs his players
		</p>




